{"questionId":"9076269","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>A ray of light travelling in an optic fibre undergoes total internal reflection at point P.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://ib-questionbank-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/tinymce_asset/asset/4703/Schermafbeelding_2018-08-11_om_06.49.40.png\" alt=\"M18/4/PHYSI/SP3/ENG/TZ1/09\"></p>\n<p>The refractive index of the core is 1.56 and that of the cladding 1.34.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Calculate the critical angle at the core−cladding boundary.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>«</strong>sin <em>c</em>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{1.34}}{{1.56}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.34</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.56</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span><strong>»</strong></p>\n<p><em>c</em> = 59.2<strong>«</strong>°<strong>»</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Accept values in the range: 59.0 to 59.5.</em></p>\n<p><em>Accept answer 1.0 rad.</em></p>\n<p><strong><em>[1 mark]</em></strong></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076269","referenceCode":"18M.3.SL.TZ1.9a","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Calculate the critical angle at the core−cladding boundary.","paper":"3","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Core topics)","C.3 – Fibre optics","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Core topics)"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}